---
// IntroSection.astro — second section on home page
// Renders different copy on desktop vs. mobile via CSS show/hide
---

<section class="intro-section">
  <div class="intro-inner">

    <!-- DESKTOP COPY -->
    <div class="intro-desktop">
      <p>
        For twenty years I carried a camera for publications like the New York Times, Washington Post, and TIME — a photojournalist trained to find the real stories underneath what people say first. The Story Speaks brings that same instinct to brand films, documentaries, and impact narratives.
      </p>

      <p>
        Five Emmys, a national Addy, and TED recognition for "Ads Worth Spreading," I work out of Boulder, Colorado — partnering with mission-driven nonprofits, leading hospitals, research universities, and Fortune 500s across Denver, the Rockies, and the world.
      </p>

      <p>
        No agency bloat. No formula. Just careful storytelling, with a crew that scales to fit your project and a budget that respects it — whether you're a global brand, a research institution, or a nonprofit fighting for something that matters.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- MOBILE COPY (shorter) -->
    <div class="intro-mobile">
      <p>
        Twenty years carrying a camera for the New York Times, Washington Post, and TIME — trained as a photojournalist to find the real story underneath what people say first.
      </p>

      <p>
        Five Emmys. A national Addy. TED-recognized work in 20+ countries. Based in Boulder, Colorado, working with mission-driven nonprofits, leading hospitals, research universities, and Fortune 500s.
      </p>

      <p>
        No agency bloat. No formula. Just careful storytelling — for a global brand, a research institution, or a nonprofit fighting for something that matters.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .intro-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Default: show desktop, hide mobile */
  .intro-desktop { display: block; }
  .intro-mobile { display: none; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .intro-section {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .intro-desktop { display: none; }
    .intro-mobile { display: block; }

    .intro-mobile p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .intro-section {
      padding: 7rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
